{"tid":1247404,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"屋企俾我呃咗，以為我信睇TVB新聞就會撞線連唔到wifi","createTime":"2019-06-21T05:50:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T15:01:02.000Z","uid":214972,"like":8,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"47317c7c452196047cedf46c1c19cb70b68e1e83","tid":1247404,"uid":214972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:50:12.000Z","msg":"早牌佢睇唔過眼兩老成日睇CCTVB啲新聞 / 財經資訊台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n次次我地一睇佢就會用手機log in屋企個router轉密碼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後我地問佢點解，佢就話：可能而家Digital signal，電視又係sony智能電視連晒wifi乜乜乜，<br />\n<br />\nTVB新聞咁多即時資訊郁郁下咁撞線都唔出奇啊，試下轉viutv嗰啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n結果我地一轉佢又轉返wifi password。我地話：真係喎，都係阿仔醒，屋企啲電子野交晒比你真係冇錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我地扮完全唔知仲信晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家索性連TVB都唔睇，佢終於肯返返匡智（之前試過用逃學威脅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e01a4f2caaeb60705e2ea698e12dcc11166e7c74","tid":1247404,"uid":200158,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T05:55:30.000Z","msg":"大家幫手 fb ig 度度都share 下<br />\n<br />\n香港是否得救，是否被林鄭秋後算帳，靠白宮聯署及G20請願。<br />\n白宮聯署是打響頭炮，簽名數字不要低得難看啊！<br />\n<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/president-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation?fbclid=IwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Fpresident-trump-please-liberate-hong-kong-communist-chinas-occupation%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0073W1w-hIjlTPtOiixjs4tthEHykqRf5VGpl80lKtBs2aDbhrxbJTzDs&d=ciq